BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Why a "Wolf Moon"? As creatures well-adapted to winter condi
 tions\, wolves are often observed howling during the crisp\, cold months
  – a behavior that is thought to reflect excitement and contentment with
  the wintry landscape.\n\nThis is the first of three supermoons for this
  year. The next ones are in November and December.
DTEND:20260103T100250Z
DTSTAMP:20260101T053147Z
DTSTART:20260103T100250Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251231T225852Z
SUMMARY:🌕 Full Supermoon (Wolf)
