BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Kartik Purnima\, a revered festival in Hinduism\, is celebra
 ted on the full moon day of the Hindu month of Kartik. This festival hol
 ds great significance as it commemorates Lord Shiva's triumph over the d
 emon Tripurasura\, and is also associated with Lord Krishna's defeat of 
 the demon Narakasura.\n\nThis auspicious day symbolizes the victory of g
 ood over evil and provides an opportunity to admire the moon’s splendor 
 and ponder its spiritual importance.
DTEND:20261124T145329Z
DTSTAMP:20260101T053147Z
DTSTART:20261124T145329Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251231T231752Z
SUMMARY:🌕 Super Full Moon (Kartik Purnima)
