DESCRIPTION:Samhain marks the last of the year's four cross-quarter fest
 ivals in the Wheel of the Year\, celebrated by many in Neopagan and Wicc
 an traditions. Positioned between the Autumn Equinox and the Winter Sols
 tice in the Northern Hemisphere\, it serves as a time to honor and remem
 ber the deceased.
